  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-w=\"1024\" data-imgfileid=\"100004869\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=48a3630f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52RibicvR6IjQz2NSSD0ibUyOHDlHXiaPOuSqSnkAQK7U0Gia4N46vppEhFe5IZlMTE91f352ia0DlKl1ibT8zA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <hr style=\"margin-left:0em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.54px;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;widows:1;margin-right:0em;\">\n  <div data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"padding-top:4px;visibility:visible;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;margin-right:0em;margin-left:0em;outline:0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);font-family:微软雅黑;margin-bottom:0px;widows:1;\">\n   <hr style=\"color: #0000007b;outline: 0px;border-style: solid;border-right-width: 0px;border-bottom-width: 0px;border-left-width: 0px;border-color: #00000015;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);visibility: visible;\">\n   <p><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: #888888;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源：</span></span></strong><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: #888888;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文为公众号</span><strong><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: #00000000;outline: 0px;color: #0000007d;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: #00000000;outline: 0px;color: #888888;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">钛媒体(taimeiti)</span></span></strong></strong><span leaf=\"\">原创首发，笔记侠经授权发布。转载请联系原公众号授权。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: #888888;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: #00000000;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: #00000000;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">分享嘉宾：</span></span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: #00000000;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span text=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: #00000000;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">陈天桥，</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: #00000000;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: #00000000;outline: 0px;\">盛大集团创始人、董事长兼CEO，天桥脑科学研究院创始人。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;text-align: right;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"color: #888888;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">责编 |&nbsp;</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:1.5em;widows:1;text-align:justify;\">贾宁</span></span><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"color: #888888;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">排版</span></strong></span><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;| 沐言</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;color: #0000007a;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;text-align: right;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0px;text-align: justify;color: #888888;font-size: 13px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">第 9372&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">篇深度好文：3918字 |11分钟阅读</span></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-left:0em;padding:10px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;margin-top:-4px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:25.6px;margin-right:0em;\">\n    <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding-bottom: 3px;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 0.15em solid #a0a0a0;display: inline-block;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 3px;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 0.15em solid #a0a0a0;display: inline-block;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.54px;\"><span leaf=\"\">思维方式</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"margin-left:0em;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0em;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:0em;padding:10px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.54px;margin-top:-4px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:25.6px;margin-right:0em;\">\n      <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n        <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n         <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration: underline;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;font-size:13px;line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">笔记君说：</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n         <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0.5em;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">你有没有想过一个问题：AI比我们更聪明、更高效、永远不累，那我们的价值到底在哪里？</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0.5em;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们身上的</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(70, 70, 70);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;&quot;,&quot;data-mp-plugin&quot;:&quot;96weixin&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;letter-spacing: 0.544px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">缺点”，比如会疲惫、会冲动、会犯错，这些真的是拖后腿的缺陷吗？</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0.5em;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">陈天桥的这篇最新文章想跟我们聊一个不一样的观点：这些所谓的“缺点”，可能恰恰是我们未来最不可替代的优势。因为我们会疼，所以我们懂得代价；因为我们“不理性”，所以我们敢赌一个伟大的可能。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0.5em;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">下面，我们就来聊聊，在AI时代，一个人真正的“铁饭碗”到底是什么。文章不长，但可能会改变你看待自己和未来的思维方式，值得一读。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;width: 556.364px;background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, rgb(160, 160, 160), rgba(255, 247, 234, 0)) rgba(174, 81, 81, 0);\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 5px 10px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一、</span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span leaf=\"\">人类的结构性防线：“碳基缺陷”</span></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在执行层面，我们因为肉体的脆弱（</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">会累、会痛、会死</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">）和决策的非理性（</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">冲动、偏见、赌性</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">），而完败给机器，我曾因此预测管理学的黄昏即将到来！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但当我们退无可退的时候，又正是这些“缺陷”奇迹般地转化成了人类不可被逾越的防线：因为肉体的脆弱，人类能懂得代价；因为决策的非理性，人类可能变得伟大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在执行层，缺陷是Bug；但在决策层，缺陷可能是Feature（特色）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100004878\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=32bc020b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Ribic3gkE65KzPy4sJygLOvyZlBGtZ7UA6WDwJB79sMIicgMTcnnLoic9MLPuuHXwibYjhXyLfy5oTlnADw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一道防线：有了肉体的脆弱，才能担责</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI的本质是计算，人类的本质是博弈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就好比德州扑克：如果桌上是虚拟筹码，依靠数学家算概率就行；但一旦押上身家性命，我们的决策就变得沉重无比，这种重量，正来源于我们肉体的“不可溯性”：我们的财富会归零，名誉会扫地，生命会终结。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 AI 因为可以在虚拟空间里无限重开，失败只是参数调整，他无法付出人类因为肉体的不可溯性而带来的代价，而代价，是商业社会交易的基础，谁承担“不可撤销”的后果，谁才拥有上牌桌的权利。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里我要澄清一个误区：</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“担责”不是背锅，而是确权。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">并不是说坏事需要人担着，好事都被AI拿走了。恰恰相反，担责意味着对结果的全权所有。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100004880\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c9d6384&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Ribic3gkE65KzPy4sJygLOvyZlFT5UPf72KwEYRj56mIq8F4EZCia1ORBsADyaw8tJKJGRdgtBYYWUgxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为只有我们能付出切肤之痛的代价，所以只有我们才有资格享受成功的百倍红利。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">AI只是拿固定工资（</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">电费/算力</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">）的打工者，而我们是拿剩余价值（</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">利润/股权</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">）的股东，</span></span></span><strong style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">痛苦是收益的门票</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">第二道防线：只有决策的非理性，才可能伟大</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">理性可能强大，因为AI的底层逻辑是基于概率论和历史数据寻找“统计学最优解”，但这也意味着AI的天性是收敛（</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">Convergence</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">）和避险。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它的任务是拉平曲线，消除噪音，让一切回归均值。但在文明进化的尺度上，“回归均值”往往等同于“平庸的死寂”，因此绝不可能伟大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">试想一下，如果15世纪有一个AI担任哥伦布的顾问，它会根据当时所有的航海数据计算出：向西航行是死路一条，它会用完美的理性劝阻哥伦布：“请留在港口，那是局部最优解”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同样，AI绝不会建议凡高画下那扭曲的星空，因为它违反了当时所有的透视学算法。在AI的算法里，哥伦布和梵高都是必须被优化掉的“噪音”、“错误”和“离群值”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但恰恰是这些“离群值”引爆了人类文明的每一次伟大的跃迁。我们之所以成为万物之灵，不是因为我们比机器更理性，而是因为我们拥有“神圣的非理性”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里我们同样要澄清一个误区，我们说的“非理性”，绝不是无知的“瞎选”，更不是把命运交给硬币的“盲目随机”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“伟大的选择”是在穷尽了所有的理性计算之后，依然选择相信那个1%可能的信念。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它是基于深刻直觉的战略冒险，它是经验积累到极致后的直觉跃迁。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100004884\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=14e3e4db&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Ribic3gkE65KzPy4sJygLOvyZlk5xryKMe1VaP1ZRTpK0Zrz1F15ZwPmUzKGnuw6fibZVMoYbtEvp4qeQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种“基于深刻洞察的主动偏离”，是碳基生命最后的火种。理性构成了我们生存的地板，但那些看似错误的“疯狂”，才是通向文明的天窗。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;width: 556.364px;background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, rgb(160, 160, 160), rgba(255, 247, 234, 0)) rgba(174, 81, 81, 0);\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 5px 10px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">二、</span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI和人类共同形成的价值闭环</span></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果人类脆弱而且还不愿意主动承担，脆弱就仅仅是软肋；只有当我们押上代价，脆弱才变成了 AI 无法生成的“信用”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果我们有“非理性”的偏离，而且从不主动选择这种偏离，偏离就仅仅是噪音；只有当我们选择这种偏离，它才变成了 AI 无法计算的“奇迹”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">选择和承担正是人类最后的防线。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;text-align:center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100004892\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9ed9f0db&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Ribic3gkE65KzPy4sJygLOvyZl8W1HJROKzibDmDWvzoxIBfHHAm5tn0icYmwX9C98wV0MJtfCCljjjQAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而对于AI来说，因为商业的本质是利益的交换，所以AI永远无法坐上主桌——它拥有永不减少的寿命，所以它付不出同等的代价；它拥有完美的逻辑，所以它给不了伟大的变异。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI就像是一个对着空气出拳的拳击手，没有人类替它选择，它只是耗散的热量， 而非物理学上的做功。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">没有人类替它“承担”，扮演价值传递的介质，AI就没有来自拳击的回馈和反作用力，只有形成了价值回馈和闭环，AI的运算才从数据处理变成了商业价值，意义才得以确立。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;width: 556.364px;background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, rgb(160, 160, 160), rgba(255, 247, 234, 0)) rgba(174, 81, 81, 0);\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 5px 10px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">三、</span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span leaf=\"\">超级个体的崛起</span></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克模式的民主化</span></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我选择，我承担”只是面对 AI 的被动防御么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">初看是的，但是深入的思考下去，会发现这其实是通往“超级个体”的进化之路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人误以为超级个体就是“全才”，这对于碳基生物来说是违背自然规律的，哪怕是马斯克，也不可能同时既是顶级的火箭专家，又是顶级的脑科学家，还是顶级的汽车工程师，但他是一个极致的“意志杠杆”。他利用他的“意志”和“信用”，聚合了全人类最优秀的外部大脑来为他做功。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克本人在这个系统里只做两件事：</span></span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">极具野心的 Prompt（</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">选择</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">）：指明那个看似不可能的方向。</span></span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">赌上一切的担责（</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">Ownership</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">）：承担所有失败的代价，这就是超级个体的定义。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有人会说：“因为马斯克有钱，所以他才能担责。” 这完全搞反了因果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克不是第一天就有钱才去担责，而是因为他之前的每一次正确决定和成功担责，撬动了今天的成就和财富。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">钱是我们过去做出的正确决定、并承担了后果之后，社会发给我们的“信任凭证”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100004882\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c100c33&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Ribic3gkE65KzPy4sJygLOvyZlNDBDF3LSz26ia5AmAbFrdeiauDnEaiatmJ0ibbnVia1bS2TbdRukTzFE7ZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">人类和AI之间将形成一个巧妙的杠杆，责任是支点， AI的执行是杠杆臂，而选择则是施力撬动的目标。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">这个杠杆会将“马斯克模式”彻底民主化，更多的超级个体将在未来不断涌现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为AI已经将执行力无限放大，人类现在唯一需要比拼的，就是谁的支点（</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">责任</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">）更稳，谁的施力（</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">选择</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">）更准。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;width: 556.364px;background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, rgb(160, 160, 160), rgba(255, 247, 234, 0)) rgba(174, 81, 81, 0);\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 5px 10px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">四、</span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span leaf=\"\">构建最小可行性责任（MVR）</span></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，在AI原生阶段，不需要人人都能成为马斯克，但我们有必要尽快构建出个人主体价值的支点，将自己从随时可被替换的“执行者”，跃迁到不可替代的“责任主体”，我把这个支点称为 MVR（</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">“最小可行性责任”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">），具体可以分为三级：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">第一级：建立“人机防火墙”，我们要做现实世界的守门人。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">哪怕AI的产出再完美，也必须经由我们的逐行检查和肉身签名。我们签下的不是名字，是信用。我们要敢于对着世界说：“此方案经我验证，我为此负责。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二级：学会“概率预测”，做好守门人后我们还要做预言家。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI只能拟合过去，而我们能直觉未来。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">试着在方案后附上我们的赌注：“我有七成的把握成功，但也做好了三成失败的准备。”这每一次的下注与复盘，都是对我们认知的一次淬火。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100004886\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=752f1c4a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Ribic3gkE65KzPy4sJygLOvyZlgo0vcANn5q3r8TRuJhUpKOZU97pOiaeheXA9OOKfAuiacTBoLIGB30hQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">第三级：主动认领“混乱”，AI 喜欢秩序，喜欢收敛。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以我们的终极使命，是拥抱混乱。去寻找那些数据缺失的角落，去解决那些人心博弈的难题。当其他人都退缩时，请举起我们的手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为我们的价值，不在于处理了多少公文，而在于解决了多少连 Prompt</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;\">（提示词）</span><span leaf=\"\">都写不出来的离散与荒谬。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">签名确权，概率预测，驾驭复杂。</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不断练习，我们就不再是冰冷的算力接口，我们成了拥有信用记录和决策能力的超级节点。而组织将进化为一个“责任容器”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它存在的唯一理由是作为一个法律实体和资本实体，去替这些超级节点承载那些一个人背不动的物理代价和无限责任。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;width: 556.364px;background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, rgb(160, 160, 160), rgba(255, 247, 234, 0)) rgba(174, 81, 81, 0);\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 5px 10px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">结语</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">至此，我已尽力呈现关于 AI 原生时代的商业拼图。但我所描绘的一切，究竟是逻辑自洽的空想，还是触手可及的未来？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了验证它，我将通过一个深度日志系列，毫无保留地公开我正在亲手打造的AI Native公司—Tanka的核心过程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我会公开我们的底层逻辑、运行蓝图，以及那些决定生死的关键争辩。无论你是见证者还是未来的同行者，请看我们如何利用AI的杠杆，试图从旧时代的泥潭中拔出双腿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果我成功了，这将是新时代的生存样本；如果我失败了，这也将是后来者宝贵的前车之鉴。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论结果如何，我选择公开。并且，我愿为可能的失败承担一切责任。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "陈天桥认为，在 AI 时代，人类的脆弱和非理性是 AI 无法替代的“护城河”，是人类实现伟大和承担责任的基石，预示着超级个体通过“选择”和“承担”与 AI 共舞的未来。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "陈天桥认为，在 AI 时代，人类的脆弱和非理性是 AI 无法替代的“护城河”，是人类实现伟大和承担责任的基石，预示着超级个体通过“选择”和“承担”与 AI 共舞的未来。",
  "summary": "陈天桥在文章中探讨了在 AI 时代人类的不可替代性，认为人类的“缺点”如肉体脆弱和非理性决策，反而构成了抵御 AI 冲击的“护城河”。他指出，人类因肉体的脆弱而懂得承担代价，从而拥有商业社会中“担责”和“确权”的资格，享受成功带来的百倍红利。而非理性决策则可能带来 AI 无法计算的伟大创新，引爆文明跃迁。文章进一步阐述了人类与 AI 将形成“马斯克模式”的杠杆，通过人类的“选择”和“承担责任”来撬动 AI 的强大执行力，实现“超级个体”的崛起。最后，陈天桥提出构建“最小可行性责任（MVR）”的三级路径：建立人机防火墙（签名确权）、学会概率预测（预言家角色）和主动认领混乱（拥抱复杂），旨在将个人从执行者转变为不可替代的主体，并预告将公开其 AI Native 公司的核心过程来验证这些观点。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "人类的“肉体脆弱”和“非理性”是 AI 无法替代的独特优势。",
      "explanation": "人类的肉体脆弱让人懂得代价，从而具备承担责任的资格，而非理性决策则能催生出超越数据逻辑的伟大创新和文明跃迁，是人类超越 AI 的结构性防线。"
    },
    {
      "point": "人类与 AI 将形成杠杆效应，通过“选择”和“承担”实现超级个体崛起。",
      "explanation": "AI 提供无限执行力，而人类则通过做出高瞻远瞩的“选择”和“承担后果”来撬动这一力量，如同“马斯克模式”般聚合资源，实现个人价值的指数级放大。"
    },
    {
      "point": "构建“最小可行性责任（MVR）”是个人在 AI 时代的核心竞争力。",
      "explanation": "通过三级路径：建立人机防火墙（对 AI 产出负责）、学会概率预测（预见未来并下注）和主动认领混乱（解决 AI 无法处理的复杂问题），将人从执行者升级为不可替代的“责任主体”。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在执行层，缺陷是 Bug；但在决策层，缺陷可能是 Feature（特色）。",
    "因为只有我们能付出切肤之痛的代价，所以只有我们才有资格享受成功的百倍红利。",
    "但恰恰是这些“离群值”引爆了人类文明的每一次伟大的跃迁。我们之所以成为万物之灵，不是因为我们比机器更理性，而是因为我们拥有“神圣的非理性”。",
    "人类和 AI 之间将形成一个巧妙的杠杆，责任是支点， AI 的执行是杠杆臂，而选择则是施力撬动的目标。",
    "未来，衡量一个人价值的，将不再是你会多少技能（AI 比你更快），而是你敢为什么事拍板，并愿意承担其所有后果。"
  ],
